title:
Quasisymmetric minimality on packing dimension for homogeneous perfect
  sets
authors: Shishuang Liu, Yanzhe Li, Jiaojiao Yang
abstract:
In this paper, we study the quasisymmetric packing minimality of homogeneous
perfect sets, and obtain that a special class of homogeneous perfect sets with
$\operatorname{dim}_{P}E=1$ is quasisymmetrically packing minimal.
